caption: The image features a bunny rabbit sitting under a Christmas tree, surrounded by presents. The rabbit is wearing a bow tie and appears to be enjoying the festive atmosphere. The scene is set against a green background, and the text "You light up my life" is displayed above the rabbit, adding a touch of warmth and joy to the image.
